description:
A sultry bronze smokey eye looks great on all skin tones and goes well with all eye colors. This video tutorial shows you how to create this smoldering look.

Products used for this look :

1. Lakme Absolute Ultimate Kohl
2. MAC eye shadow : Bronze (shimmery bronze)
3. Bourjois Intense Extrait eye shadow : 09 (matte dark brown)
4. MAC eye shadow : Ricepaper (pale gold highlighter)
5.Sleek Brow kit : Extra Dark
6. Maybelline The Falsies Volum'Express Mascara
7. Inglot eye lash curler

Lenses : http://www.kiwiberry1-collection.com/...
